        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2157109781" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8705177354525227856">I have been wanting to read a biography of Theodore Roosevelt for years now, but there was always something more important and urgent to read to. So when the time came i decided to go for overkill and to read (listen on audible, to be exact) a three-part biography that has 2500 pages in total. This is a first, 780 pages long part. <br/><br/>If what you&apos;ve read doesn&apos;t scare you, maybe consider reading it however make sure that you are committed to 2500 pages or ~80 hours of audiobook listening. So far I&apos;m</span>
  <span id="freeText8705177354525227856" style="display:none">I have been wanting to read a biography of Theodore Roosevelt for years now, but there was always something more important and urgent to read to. So when the time came i decided to go for overkill and to read (listen on audible, to be exact) a three-part biography that has 2500 pages in total. This is a first, 780 pages long part. <br /><br />If what you've read doesn't scare you, maybe consider reading it however make sure that you are committed to 2500 pages or ~80 hours of audiobook listening. So far I'm enjoying it tremendously. <br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="8705177354525227856" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

