<li class='cover' id='bookCover_40923'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/40923.Theodore_Rex"><img alt="Theodore Rex" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388177930l/40923._SY75_.jpg" />
